{
  "texts": [
    "We use QAOA with p = 1 and the xy mixer given by B = 1 2 N j=1 (x j x j+1 + y j y j+1) and set the initial state |s⟩ to be the uniform superposition over all Hamming weight k states (Dicke state).",
    "We denote this variant xy-QAOA.We first observe that the rescaling improves the optimization landscape.",
    "The QAOA energy at p 1 is presented in Figure 4.",
    "The landscape with the original objective function (Figure 4a,b) is flat, making the optimization difficult.",
    "After rescaling (Figure 4c), a clear local minimum is visible."
  ]
}